description: City - Bangor, MEIt's not just a Burrito, a Taco or a Bowl. It's a hunger. It's a passion. It's handcrafted, great, delicious food on the go. Stay curious and branch away from Burgers & Co. to try something new!. Create your own perfect meal, unique, fresh and devilishly delicious. Be hungry and curious with the Cielos Truck.Be "Cielosworthy", and come find us on the street!
